# n8n Discord Nodes - Project Overview

This is a community node package for n8n that provides Discord integration capabilities. The package includes nodes to trigger workflows from Discord or send interactive messages using Discord's components API.

## Key Features

- Two-way communication with Discord using a bot (no webhooks)
- Interactive message components (buttons, selects)
- Trigger workflows from Discord messages, commands, and events
- Send rich messages with embeds, buttons, and selects
- User presence and role management

## Main Files

- Main node definitions:
  - [src/nodes/Discord/Discord.node.ts](mdc:src/nodes/Discord/Discord.node.ts) - The Discord Send node
  - [src/nodes/Discord/DiscordTrigger.node.ts](mdc:src/nodes/Discord/DiscordTrigger.node.ts) - The Discord Trigger node
  
- Node configuration options:
  - [src/nodes/Discord/Discord.node.options.ts](mdc:src/nodes/Discord/Discord.node.options.ts)
  - [src/nodes/Discord/DiscordTrigger.node.options.ts](mdc:src/nodes/Discord/DiscordTrigger.node.options.ts)

- Bot implementation:
  - [src/nodes/Discord/bot/](mdc:src/nodes/Discord/bot) - Contains the Discord bot implementation

- Credentials:
